Package: VaRisk
Type: Package
Title: VaR (Value at Risk) of your Portfolio
Version: 1.1
Date: 2019-05-10
Author: c(person("Kevin","Moroni",email = "moronk@usi.ch",role = c("aut","trl", "cre")),
